Erling Haaland's Future "Became A Dressing Room Burden": Borussia Dortmund Sporting Director

Sebastian Kehl, who played 362 games with Dortmund and won three Bundesliga titles, said Erling Haaland's departure "represented an opportunity for us as a team".

Borussia Dortmund skipper Sebastian Kehl out for six weeks

The 33-year-old landed heavily on his right ankle in training on Sunday, while a scan has revealed torn ankle ligaments and he is expected to be out until the end of October for last season's Champions League finalists.
